CODE:
```
flowchart TD
    subgraph "Backend"
        API["Rest API"]
        POSTGRESQL["PostgreSQL"]
        REDIS["Redis"]
        S3["S3 Storage"]
        WORKER["Worker"]
        WORKER_GITHUB["Worker GitHub"]
    end
    subgraph "Frontend"
        WEB["Web client"]
    end
    GITHUB_WH["GitHub Webhooks"]
    STRIPE_WH["Stripe Webhooks"]
    USERS["Users"]

    WEB --> API
    API --> POSTGRESQL
    API --> REDIS
    REDIS <--> WORKER
    REDIS <--> WORKER_GITHUB
    WORKER --> POSTGRESQL
    WORKER_GITHUB --> POSTGRESQL
    API --> S3
    WEB --> S3

    GITHUB_WH -.-> API
    STRIPE_WH -.-> API
    USERS -.-> API
    USERS -.-> WEB
```

